# Event Support Dashboard — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# GOOGLE SHEET LIVE CONNECTION
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# HOW TO GET YOUR URL:
#   1. Open your Google Sheet
#   2. File → Share → Publish to web
#   3. First dropdown: choose your sheet tab (e.g. "Sheet1")
#   4. Second dropdown: choose "Comma-separated values (.csv)"
#   5. Click "Publish" → copy the URL shown
#   6. Paste it below (remove the # at the start)
#
# REACT_APP_SHEET_CSV_URL=https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/YOUR_SHEET_ID/pub?gid=0&single=true&output=csv
#
# If this is left blank, the app uses the static data in src/data/teamData.js
